stories.title: Wasim Akram helps Pakistan to solid total
stories.summary: Pakistan veteran Wasim Akram celebrated his share of a world record in one-day international cricket tonight with a thumping finish to the visitors' innings against Australia in the deciding one-day international clash at the Gabba.
